Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:02.60,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{Sort by Time}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even fate can be used\Nas a hint for reasoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.11,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing through the\Nmost mysterious cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:08.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Genta's the lead actor today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He might not be all that reliable as a friend,\Nbut we're all following him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.74,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:40.53,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{Timeshift -427 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:44.00,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Teitan Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody, dig in!\NI don't want to see any picky eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A teenage boy eating\Nwith grade-school kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Personally,\NI'm enjoying the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Growing up in the States, everybody\Nhelped themselves at the school cafeteria,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I usually ended up\Neating alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's intriguing how Japanese schools\Nfoster a sense of community.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, this was fun\Nthe first time around...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nyou left your carrots again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm just saving\Nthem for last!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:23.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's always somebody who picks out\Nthe vegetables he doesn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:30.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And there's always a dumb guy who brags\Nabout being the fastest eater in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course, in this class,\Nit's always...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray! I'm number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:37.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He beat Genta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r},\NI'm not feeling too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I go down\Nto the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} left most\Nof his lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!\NYou know him and food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nhasn't played with us for a couple of days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's been going\Nstraight home after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe an upperclassman\Nis bullying him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Genta's not the kind\Nof guy who'd get bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if he was,\Nhe'd be safer sticking with us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a problem\Nwith his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone in\Nhis family is gravely ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or his parents\Nare fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't do anything\Nabout death or divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His parents are fine!\NThey're still happily running their liquor store!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried, so I dropped by\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s house yesterday to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it sounds like Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nis afraid of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His parents told me he was shivering\Ninside his futon the moment he got home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is he scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept getting, "It's nothing",\Nno matter how many times I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he might\Ntell his friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me\Nif he opens up to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nbehind our backs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you practicing\Nto become a ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! You skipped lunch\Nto slim down for ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw this cool ninja flick\Nthe other day and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why were you shivering\Nunder the covers at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you had a nightmare about\Nbeing attacked by a bloody samurai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and you're training to\Nfight your imaginary enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I... The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-My life is in danger!\NA hitman's out to get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hitman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would a hitman want\Nto kill an elementary school kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right... Unless it was me or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it was dumb\Nto tell you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:06:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Ntell us the whole story!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was walking through that\Ntunnel under the train tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I heard these\Nfootsteps behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see\Nanything in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when I stopped, he'd stop,\Nand when I ran, he ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably just the echo of your\Nfootsteps against the tunnel wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, somebody pushed me\Ndown the stairs on the overpass,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and yesterday a motorbike\Nran a red light and almost hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A big bolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where could it\Nhave fallen from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's from that\Ndepartment store sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bolt just happened\Nto rust out, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just having a bad day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, maybe you should go to a shrine\Nand have them do a purifying ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... This was more\Nthan just luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cord on this neon sign\Nwas cut with a sharp object.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone deliberately cut it before\Nloosening the bolt, to drop the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's true, maybe it was just a crazy guy\Nattacking anybody who passed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I think there\Nwas a specific target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the Kamen Yaiba capsule machine\NGenta's always drooling over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then he really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Looks like Genta's life\Nreally {\i1}is{\i0} in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better tell us\Neverything, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you a target?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw the serial snatcher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crook who's been snatching bags\Nfrom old people and unsuspecting women?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you tell the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... About a week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see the wanted\Nposters until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They asked where I'd seen\Nthe guy on the posters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and by that time I'd forgotten\Nwhere I saw the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then I saw a guy\Nwho saw the snatcher with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saw him with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five days ago, the snatcher\Nattacked a woman by my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I dropped by\Nthe crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when I saw\Nhim in the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blond guy who was near me\Nwhen I saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I grabbed him by the hand\Nand took him to the nearest cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the guy said he didn't\Nremember me or the snatcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure\Nhe was the same guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. When I saw the snatcher,\NI think that guy was sitting near me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he must've\Nseen the snatcher too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was really sleepy then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I swear that\Nblond guy was nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he was there too.\NOr maybe he wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where you'd get\Nsleepy after sitting down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A movie theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or inside a train...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the look of things, the blond guy is probably\Nworking with the person targeting Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:10:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. Why didn't you tell\Nthe police you were in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I got a phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you say anything about me, you're dead!\NAnd your friends and family too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why you didn't\Ntell anybody until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is going\Nfrom bad to worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he knows your phone number,\Nhe must know where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If we went\Nto the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the snatcher might think\NGenta remembered something,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there's no telling\Nwhat he'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might even be spying\Non us this very minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember anything\Nthat might help us look for the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already told the cops,\Nbut he was smoking a cigarette with his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the snatcher\Nis left-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was wearing\Na weird T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was black with\Na skull and numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That one! That one!\NIt was just like that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you the snatcher\Nwho's after Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. He doesn't look\Nlike the guy I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the snatcher's T-shirt\Ndidn't say "1999".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It said "202"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you remember\Nwhere you got that T-shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shop by the train station\Ncalled Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NThe skull shirt is an original from our shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've put out a lot of versions,\Nbut I don't remember one that said "202".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What other versions are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"1999", "HELP", "ESCAPE"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lots of dangerous-sounding words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You remember back in 1999,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when everyone was talking about\Nend-of-the-millennium prophecies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we\Ndid a 1999 shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember any suspicious-looking\Npeople buying those T-shirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno. It's been a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I don't really remember\Nall our customers' faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that didn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} could at least remember\Nwhere he saw the snatcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could try movie theaters\Nand trains!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. You can't smoke\Nin those places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! You must've gotten sleepy\Nfrom eating too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that guy\Nwasn't eating anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was watching him\Nthe whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I just remember him reading\Na newspaper and smoking a cigarette...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come you can remember all that,\Nbut not where you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beats me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't he get annoyed at you\Nfor staring at him for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, our eyes never met...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's where they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The skull T-shirt\Nwith the number 202...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And a place where your eyes\Nwould never meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:16.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and you wouldn't attract attention\Nfor staring at someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've got it, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The very place\Nyou saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The optician's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where you\Nsaw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said he didn't get upset\Neven though you were staring at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't see you staring at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he'd taken his glasses off\Nto have them fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never been\Nto an optician's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's got to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all,\Nit'd also have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Seriously?\NI thought I'd cracked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you call yourself\Nthe modern-day Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now.\NEven a genius makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't feel down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me if you remember anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where could it be?\NThe place Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} saw the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where you can stare at somebody\Nwithout getting in trouble, and also get sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's school!\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} always falls asleep there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the snatcher was at our school,\Nwe'd have seen him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, for crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never stop eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to put on weight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares?\NI like to snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got ice cream on your face,\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you remember something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three chicken and four liver, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just have\Nsome ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,French food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show some self-control!\NYou're almost home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red... White... Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NThat's the French flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen the colors\Nred, white and blue anywhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s always wearing a red bowtie,\Nwhite shirt and blue jacket...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is he the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.\NWould Conan do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but the colors\Nred, white and blue keep spinning in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget\Nto go straight home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you get any fatter,\Neven the piggies will laugh at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid Ayumi,\Ncalling me fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not that fat, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember!\NIt was back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seventh floor of\Nthe building above the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The elevator...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, stop! Hold that elevator!\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which floor, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The s-seventh floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're that blond... guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about forgetting you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remembered where it was!\NWhere you and me saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could be\Nlistening in on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you remember too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's talk it over\Nbefore we go to the cops,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and make sure we've got\Nour stories straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere safe\Nfrom other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I think the name he wrote\Nin our schedule book was Someda...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't knock off\Nthe accusations, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left-handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A T-shirt with a skull\Nand the number 202...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No wonder the police couldn't\Npin down the snatcher's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta was looking at your\Nreflection in a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're the kids from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you never got angry at Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nfor staring at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he was watching you\Nin the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "202" he saw written\Non your T-shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was actually "SOS"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the left hand\Nwas really your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where Genta would go that has\Na mirror in front of the customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and where he could get sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the barber shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta didn't realize you and\Nthe snatcher were the same person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you had your hair\Nbleached while he was napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A guy with a black hair and glasses\Nchanged into a blond guy without glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Genta didn't see your clothes\Nbecause they were covered with a smock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He misremembered you\Nas two different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about,\Nyou little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an eyewitness\Nstanding right behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The barber who\Ndyed your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been lucky until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As it happens,\Nthe barber doesn't watch TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the police haven't posted\Nyour picture in his neighborhood yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dyed your hair black with coloring\Nthat could be washed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you thought\Nno one would recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the police got the snatcher's fingerprints\Noff the last bag he tried to snatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If those prints match yours,\Nyou can't talk your way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So what was this kid\Ndoing back in this neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luring you here,\Nthat's what!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had him get ice cream on his face\Nthat looked like shaving cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and stare at the French flag, which is\Nred, white and blue like a barber pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he stared\Nat his reflection...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,like he was looking\Nin a barber's mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We knew all along\Nthat you were following us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we convinced Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nto play dumb—no difficult task—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and lure you into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kids think\Nyou can mess with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What're you doing,\Nyou old broad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're pretty dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really think I'd walk all over town\Njust to lure you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...\NLook around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Genta bought us some time,\Nwe made a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is\Nswarming with cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's how the\Nsnatcher got arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:07.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the case closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe the words\Ncoming out of your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really a grade-schooler,\NConan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just imitating\Nthe detectives on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A huge victory for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're so lazy, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you totally fell asleep\Nwhile the snatcher was having his hair dyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The barber said he didn't wake me up\Nbecause I looked so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess they say sleep\Nis good for growing kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you were right\Nand the criminal wasn't really left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was pretty sure it wasn't {\i1}him{\i0},\Nsince he'd target me before Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it did shake me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know?\NThen here's another factoid for your files.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin is left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:50.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:55.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he wanted to see\Nwhat was inside this attaché case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the key\Nis still in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.17,0:24:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:18.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.06,0:24:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Cellular phone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:28.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:24.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:27.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,How could the great Kogoro Mouri—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.19,0:24:28.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
